    "description": "天線為輻射電磁波之元件.天線的工作原理及應用為rf工程師必備之專業知識之一.天線的參數及物理意義亦為重點",
    "prerequisites": "Electromagnetics, Advanced Mathematics, circuit theory",
    "syllabus": {
        "zh": "簡介<br>天線基礎<br>天線種類<br>點源<br>陣列天線<br>電偶極與薄的線性天線<br>迴路天線<br>槽孔,微帶 及號角天線<br>天線量測<br>第一章\t引論<br>第二章\t天線基礎<br>第三章\t天線家族<br>第四章\t點源<br>第五章(上)點源陣<br>第五章(下)點源陣<br>第六章   電偶極子和細直天線<br>第七章\t   環天線<br>第八章\t天線量測<br>第九章  微帶天線<br>第十章  無線應用之印刷天線<br>",
        "en": "Chapter\t1\tIntroduction<br>Chapter\t2\tAntenna Basics<br>Chapter\t3\tThe Antenna Family<br>Chapter\t4\tPoint Sources<br>Chapter\t5\tArrays of Point Sources, Part I<br>Chapter\t6\tThe Electric Dipole and Thin Linear Antennas<br>Chapter\t7\tThe Electric Dipole and Thin Linear Antennas<br>Chapter\t8\tAntenna Measurements.  <br>Chapter 9    Microstrip antennas<br>Chapter 10   Printed antennas for wireless application<br><br>"
    },
